{
  "stem": "13251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, when I was single, I-- I loved to travel, so I went to Europe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the first year or so, maybe it was a year and a half, and in fact, for three months-- I dragged it out to six months [LAUGHS] because I stayed in England longer with some friends-- anyway, when the money ran out sort of, I came back to Cleveland.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was really-- I-- I felt very independent, because I had a good profession.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think I made a-- like, three or four phone calls, and I got a job, paid me more money than I-- that I abandoned.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- so there was no sweat about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, I just got back, and one of my friends in Cleveland happened to have, just perfect timing, he got married.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I-- so I was invited, and I went to his wedding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he came from a poor family, I mean, you know, not well-off family, neither one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So instead of having an evening wedding, they had an afternoon wedding, which was less expensive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the wedding was over by the evening, and here I'm all dressed up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What am I going to do, go home?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to a social at the Jewish Community Center, and that's where I met my wife.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And her name?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Helene.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rudolph, ?] Helene [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rudolph, ?] yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, when I met her-- the way I met her is one of the girls at the-- at the Jewish Community Center, Sandy-- I'd-- I-- I knew from before from the socials-- and she says, hey, you know Helene.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd met Helene once visiting somebody who was babysitting, [LAUGHS] and she was, I think, like, 15, 16 at the time, OK?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a couple years earlier.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
